- @page_title = "Add-ons: Logo"

%h2= @page_title

:textile
  The Logo add-on has one free tier that allows you to define the position of the SublimeVideo logo.

  The second tier of the Logo add-on allows you to disable the SublimeVideo logo while the third tier allows you to display your own custom logo.

  h3. Settings

  The following settings respect the "Player settings syntax":player-settings.

